software.leonov.util.gson.factory

Class MultisetTypeAdapterFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • software.leonov.util.gson.factory.MultisetTypeAdapterFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TypeAdapterFactory

    public final class MultisetTypeAdapterFactory
extends Object
implements TypeAdapterFactory
    Creates TypeAdapters for serializing and deserializing Multiset values to and from JSON.

    Supported Multiset Types:

    • LinkedHashMultiset (default for deserialization)
    • HashMultiset
    • TreeMultiset
    • ConcurrentHashMultiset

    Serialization/Deserialization Behavior:

    All supported Multiset implementations can be serialized to JSON. Attempting to deserialize unsupported Multiset implementations will result in an IllegalArgumentException.

    Author:
    Zhenya Leonov
